    "Our results should be interpreted in view of several limitations.",
    "The first relates to the difference in the number of PLSs in each group.",
    "Cochrane is the most prominent organization publishing PLSs for systematic reviews in the field of medicine, and PLSs are mandatory for all systematic reviews in the Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews 38.",
